                                    Habitat for Humanity of Greater Nashville


                                    Habitat has partnered with the two Universities to provide guidance in construction as well as energy saving measures. On top of taking ownership of the home after the competition, Habitat hopes to use Harmony House as a model for affordable solar powered housing in the future.

                                    For more information on Habitat for Humanity of Greater Nashville, be sure to visit their website, and for updates on our builds with Habitat, keep up with our blog.
